VALIDATE_ADDRESS (triggered by input)
  ├─ empty/undefined           → EMPTY_INPUT
  ├─ incomplete                → INCOMPLETE_ADDRESS
  ├─ invalid hex/address       → INVALID_ADDRESS_INPUT  (or INVALID_HEX_INPUT if you split)
  └─ valid                     → TEST_DUPLICATE_INPUT

EMPTY_INPUT                     → (do nothing / clear previews)

INCOMPLETE_ADDRESS              → show ErrorAssetPreview
INVALID_HEX_INPUT               → show ErrorAssetPreview
INVALID_ADDRESS_INPUT           → show ErrorAssetPreview

TEST_DUPLICATE_INPUT
  ├─ duplicate                 → DUPLICATE_INPUT_ERROR (show ErrorAssetPreview)
  └─ ok                        → VALIDATE_LOCAL_NATIVE_TOKEN

VALIDATE_LOCAL_NATIVE_TOKEN
  → VALIDATE_EXISTS_ON_CHAIN

VALIDATE_EXISTS_ON_CHAIN
  ├─ not on chain              → CONTRACT_NOT_FOUND_ON_BLOCKCHAIN (show ErrorAssetPreview)
  └─ on chain                  → RESOLVE_ERC20_ASSET

RESOLVE_ERC20_ASSET
  ├─ resolve error             → VALIDATE_ERC20_ASSET_ERROR (show ErrorAssetPreview)
  └─ resolve ok                → (branch on manualEntry)
        • manualEntry === true   → VALIDATE_PREVIEW (show RenderAssetPreview, await click)
        • manualEntry === false  → RETURN_VALIDATED_ASSET → CLOSE_SELECT_PANEL

VALIDATE_PREVIEW                → (user sees preview; no auto-commit)
RETURN_VALIDATED_ASSET          → (bridge commits to context)
CLOSE_SELECT_PANEL              → (bridge closes & resets)
